stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle: System Start
    
    Idle --> CheckingContext: User Query
    
    CheckingContext --> ContextualReference: reference_prev_locations = True AND last_location exists
    CheckingContext --> NormalRouting: No contextual reference
    
    ContextualReference --> MCPCall: Reuse last_location
    MCPCall --> ResponseSent: Weather data returned
    ResponseSent --> Idle: Ready for next query
    
    NormalRouting --> AwaitingLocation: awaiting_location = True
    NormalRouting --> RouteDecision: awaiting_location = False
    
    AwaitingLocation --> LocationConfirmation: Force MCP with last_intent
    
    LocationConfirmation --> StillAmbiguous: Status = AMBIGUOUS
    LocationConfirmation --> LocationFound: Status = OK
    LocationConfirmation --> LocationError: Status = NOT_FOUND
    
    StillAmbiguous --> AwaitingLocation: Keep awaiting_location = True, Ask for clarification
    
    LocationFound --> ResetState: Set awaiting_location = False, Save location info
    ResetState --> ResponseSent
    
    LocationError --> Idle: Return error message
    
    RouteDecision --> RAGRoute: Keywords match RAG
    RouteDecision --> MCPRoute: Keywords match MCP
    RouteDecision --> LLMRoute: No specific keywords
    
    RAGRoute --> RAGProcess: run_research_agent
    RAGProcess --> ResponseSent: Return answer
    RAGProcess --> LLMFallback: Info not available
    LLMFallback --> ResponseSent
    
    MCPRoute --> MCPProcess: run_mcp WEATHER
    
    MCPProcess --> AmbiguousLocation: Status = AMBIGUOUS
    MCPProcess --> WeatherFound: Status = OK
    MCPProcess --> LocationNotFound: Status = NOT_FOUND
    
    AmbiguousLocation --> SetAwaitingState: awaiting_location = True, last_intent = WEATHER
    SetAwaitingState --> ResponseSent: Ask for confirmation
    
    WeatherFound --> ResponseSent: Return weather data
    LocationNotFound --> ResponseSent: Return error
    
    LLMRoute --> DirectLLM: gemini.generate_content
    DirectLLM --> ResponseSent
    
    note right of AwaitingLocation
        STATE ACTIVE
        System menunggu
        konfirmasi lokasi
        dari user
    end note
    
    note right of ResetState
        STATE RESET
        Location confirmed
        System ready for
        contextual follow-up
    end note
    
    note right of ContextualReference
        CONTEXT DETECTED
        User references
        previous location
    end note